                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, M</hi> 183). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted March</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">and confined three months, and whipped</hi>)—I was present at the trial—the prisoner is the person.</p>
